  "instructions": [
    "In a medium saucepan, heat the sesame oil over low heat.",
    "Add the grated ginger and cook for 1-2 minutes, until fragrant.",
    "Add the bhuna paste and cook for another minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the stock and coconut milk, and bring to a simmer.",
    "Add the oats and cook for 20-25 minutes, stirring occasionally, until the oats have broken down and the porridge has thickened.",
    "Stir in the soy sauce, sugar, and sesame seeds.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve the porridge hot, garnished with chopped green onion and sesame seeds."
